00:08:20.180 --> 00:08:23.670 position:56%
And they're very -- it's
interesting to say she's a Brazilian

00:08:23.670 --> 00:08:24.970
or she's not a Brazilian.

00:08:24.970 --> 00:08:27.490
They're very Brazilian, the
stories are actually more Brazilian

00:08:27.490 --> 00:08:28.960
than the novels.

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:33.540
I mean it's very much, these
women almost always women,

00:08:33.540 --> 00:08:36.770
living in a couple of
neighborhoods in Rio,

00:08:36.770 --> 00:08:40.670
and almost always doing
pretty much the same thing,

00:08:40.670 --> 00:08:44.800
which is having their
peaceful lives interrupted

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:47.050
by some violent something.

00:08:47.050 --> 00:08:49.560
And it's very rarely a
violent event, like a shooting

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:50.860
or a murder or something.

00:08:50.860 --> 00:08:52.550
It's something that
happens inside them.

00:08:52.550 --> 00:08:55.200
It's something that
touches them somehow.

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:58.290
And what's interesting,
