00:09:15.210 --> 00:09:18.510
But it's part of a series that's
now, this is now the seventh book

00:09:18.510 --> 00:09:22.270
of this series, so there's five
of the novels that we've published

00:09:22.270 --> 00:09:24.360
in English, and now the stories,

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:28.660
